<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Mar1928"><font color="red">21 March 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): The revision of <font face="wake">D</font>a nearly flattened me out so I left for here for a week or so. I hope you got the MS. Two copies of T12 are being sent you, can you check one by the MS and return it to me at Paris. My evidence against Roth was taken as you see by the N.Y.H. </div>
